\ float-specialized arithmetic — same results as generic
2 3 +f .
10 4 -f .
6 7 *f .
20 5 /f .

\ +f only consumes top two (verifies in-place behaviour)
99 2 3 +f . .

\ /f rejects division by zero
1 0 /f

\ fused multiply-add: ( a b c -- a*b+c )
